{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=675fe6e21fee057d1dca063b5f6ad007&src=http%3A%2F%2Fc.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F4a36acaf2edda3ccae35130c09e93901203f92cd.jpg","summary":"广西外国语学院坐落在广西壮族自治区首府——南宁，是一所经教育部批准成立的全日制民办本科学校，前身是广西东方外语职业学院，成立于2004年；2011年4月，经教育部下文批准同意将广西东方外语职业学院升格为本科高校并更名为广西外国语学院。据2018年4月官网显示，学校占地面积2315亩，校舍面积33万多平方米，在校师生15000人，其中国外留学生310人，建有25000平方米的先进数字化图书馆，77个专业实验室，64个实践教学基地，其中国外实践教学基地9个，馆藏图书153万册，还拥有覆盖全校的计算机网络、自主学习中心、校园双语电视台、6种语言国际同声传译实验室等现代化教学科研设施。","tags":["语言类","本科","民办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2004","所在地区":"广西南宁市青秀区五合大道19号","院校隶属":"广西自治区教育厅"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=1b4b2a4a7c4ad2a04fdff62cfc7214e9&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3655476204%2C3954871483%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=5bf85e78552f120f8ed6276129dd4e2f&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2342428143%2C2598867014%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=d1ad672bf70a6caef3bee763e94c9cca&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3668415730%2C615552787%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=9cbf223b05932226217702b436aea16d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3708493497%2C847096067%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534504139&di=8c5b789c496126441e0bf0ba500a3e9f&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3689667090%2C845343704%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_30